cu.explanation_en: Setting Num_Threads_PUSCH to 0 will disable PUSCH processing threads and cause uplink data transmission failures.

du.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause ASN.1 encoding/decoding errors and prevent proper message handling.
du.explanation_zh: 將 Asn1_verbosity 設定為無效值 'invalid' 會導致 ASN.1 編碼/解碼錯誤，並阻止正確的消息處理。
